  this.getValidPerformanceIssues(raw.performanceIssues as any[]);



Now the key problem
	â€¢	You filled only issue in the 4th row
	â€¢	timeline, standard, currentAssessment are empty
	â€¢	That row fails the filter
	â€¢	perfIssuesForSave becomes empty array []

Then this logic runs later:

