â¸»

3ï¸âƒ£ Why full row works but partial row doesnâ€™t

Case	Result
All fields filled	Passes filter â†’ saved
Only â€œPerformance Issueâ€ filled	Fails filter â†’ dropped
Empty rows	Dropped
Draft save	Uses same strict filter

Important:
