Thatâ€™s the real design issue.

â¸»

4ï¸âƒ£ Minimal & safe fix (BEST approach)

âœ… Allow partial rows ONLY for Draft

ğŸ”§ Minimal change: pass status into the validator

Step 1: Update function signature

private getValidPerformanceIssues(
  raw: any[],
  allowPartial = false
): any[] {
  return raw
    .filter(issue => {
      if (allowPartial) {
        return issue.issue?.trim();
      }
      return (
        issue.timeline &&
        issue.issue?.trim() &&
        issue.standard?.trim() &&
        issue.currentAssessment?.trim()
      );
    })
    .map(issue => ({
      ...issue,
      timeline: issue.timeline
        ? this.displayToIso(issue.timeline)
        : null
    }));
}


â¸»

