2ï¸âƒ£ Green theme NOT applied

Reason:
	â€¢	Your previous CSS did not override PrimeNG defaults
	â€¢	PrimeNG requires strong selectors (.p-button, .p-tabview, .p-card)
	â€¢	Also your app uses global header + tab layout, so spacing broke

