âœ… Correct for PrimeNG

(onChange)="onEmployeeSelected($event.value)"

âš ï¸ This is correct ONLY AFTER DropdownModule is imported
Otherwise Angular treats it as a normal DOM event.

â¸»

âœ… STEP 3: Correct HTML dropdown code (FINAL)

