What you want for Check-in Dates is the SAME PATTERN as Performance Issues, implemented cleanly with a FormArray, max 8 items, add (+) and remove (Ã—), PrimeNG inputs, validations, and inline errors.

Below is a drop-in, production-ready solution that does NOT disturb your existing form.

â¸»

âœ… WHAT YOU WILL ADD (OVERVIEW)
	â€¢	New FormArray â†’ checkInSessions
	â€¢	Each session = FormGroup
	â€¢	Max sessions = 8
