â¸»

1ï¸âƒ£ Validation rules (strong, tester-level)

Rules applied
	â€¢	UID â†’ exactly 6 characters, alphanumeric
	â€¢	Names â†’ only letters + space (NO /, @, numbers)
	â€¢	Email â†’ valid email
	â€¢	Department / Position â†’ letters + space
	â€¢	Textareas â†’ minimum length
	â€¢	Submit â†’ enabled, but submission blocked if invalid
	â€¢	Red border + error text appears
