â¸»

ğŸ” Common Causes

Cause	Fix
ğŸ”¸ Youâ€™re using a wrong Angular version with incompatible packages	Ensure youâ€™re using the correct versions of AG-Grid + Angular
ğŸ”¸ Your Angular app is missing @angular/compiler or itâ€™s outdated	Install it: npm install @angular/compiler
ğŸ”¸ You installed AG-Grid packages not compatible with Angular 17	Use the latest AG-Grid that supports Angular 17
ğŸ”¸ Your component is not using standalone: true properly	Make sure itâ€™s declared correctly


â¸»

